1
00:00:05,200 --> 00:00:06,560
I don't know

2
00:00:06,560 --> 00:00:08,240
why he's been getting involved with you.

3
00:00:08,240 --> 00:00:10,120
But I think he's probably been manipulating you.

4
00:00:10,920 --> 00:00:12,160
Just like he's done to other people.

5
00:00:13,280 --> 00:00:14,080
The one who's been putting ideas

6
00:00:14,080 --> 00:00:15,120
into your head.

7
00:00:15,120 --> 00:00:16,600
Isn't me.

8
00:00:16,600 --> 00:00:19,400
But it's probably someone who hates me.

9
00:00:19,400 --> 00:00:20,680
I...

10
00:00:20,680 --> 00:00:22,120
want to make a blood pact with you.

11
00:00:22,640 --> 00:00:23,680
I want to ask you

12
00:00:23,960 --> 00:00:25,320
to leave Jane alone.

13
00:00:25,600 --> 00:00:26,600
You do know, don't you,

14
00:00:26,600 --> 00:00:27,600
what someone like me

15
00:00:27,600 --> 00:00:28,840
is capable of doing to you?

16
00:00:29,560 --> 00:00:30,160
That's enough!

17
00:00:30,920 --> 00:00:31,880
Wasn't this necklace  supposed to be a promise

18
00:00:31,880 --> 00:00:34,040
that you'd always tell me the truth?

19
00:00:35,200 --> 00:00:36,120
I'm sure

20
00:00:36,400 --> 00:00:38,440
that one day, you'll be like them.

21
00:00:38,680 --> 00:00:39,800
You..

22
00:00:39,800 --> 00:00:40,680
will be the one crawling back

23
00:00:40,680 --> 00:00:42,680
to ask me for something.

24
00:01:19,560 --> 00:01:20,120
I think..

25
00:01:20,120 --> 00:01:21,600
I did the right thing,

26
00:01:22,280 --> 00:01:23,280
breaking up with him.

27
00:01:27,320 --> 00:01:28,960
Why does it hurt so bad?

28
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:10,240
Just cry it out.

29
00:02:22,920 --> 00:02:24,600
I'll be right here.

30
00:02:49,760 --> 00:02:54,200
You walk in with a warning sign

31
00:02:56,560 --> 00:03:01,680
Just one look and already falling for you

32
00:03:03,880 --> 00:03:09,000
My friends tell me not to cross that line

33
00:03:11,040 --> 00:03:16,120
But I’m already out of time

34
00:03:17,920 --> 00:03:20,160
I know the truth, I taste the sin

35
00:03:20,160 --> 00:03:21,760
It’s wrong but I don’t want it to be true

36
00:03:21,760 --> 00:03:24,360
I’m losing all my discipline

37
00:03:24,360 --> 00:03:28,240
You’re all I’m thinking of

38
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:30,360
and I’m breaking all the rules

39
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:32,680
just because…

40
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:35,960
You’re a red flag but I’m colorblind

41
00:03:35,960 --> 00:03:39,680
I know you’re dangerous

42
00:03:40,040 --> 00:03:43,240
If it burns, let it burn me alive

43
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:48,240
I can't hold myself back, I’d cross every line

44
00:03:53,160 --> 00:03:56,560
Ooh

45
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:08,760
I think from now on

46
00:05:08,760 --> 00:05:10,120
I will believe in myself

47
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:12,200
because you're the one

48
00:05:12,200 --> 00:05:13,680
who told me to believe in myself

49
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:18,200
that's why I entered the competition.

50
00:05:19,320 --> 00:05:20,480
I'm glad

51
00:05:22,080 --> 00:05:23,960
that I could inspire you.

52
